<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-aFq/bzH65dt+w6FI2ooMVUpc+21e0SRygnTpmBvdBgSdnuTN7QbdgL+OapgHtvPp" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <style>
    .feature-icon {
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
    border-radius: .75rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('_navout') %>

  <div class="my-5">
    <div class="p-5 text-center bg-body-tertiary">
      <div class="container py-5">
        <h1 class="text-body-emphasis">About MoodMinder</h1>

        <p class="col-lg-8 mx-auto lead">Welcome to MoodMinder, your go-to app for tracking and managing your emotions! Our mission is to provide you with a user-friendly and effective tool to monitor your mood, gain insights into your emotional well-being, and improve your overall mental health.</p>

        <p class="col-lg-8 mx-auto lead">At MoodMinder, we believe in the power of self-awareness and reflection. By regularly tracking your emotions, you can identify patterns, set goals, and take positive steps towards a healthier and happier life.</p>

        <p class="col-lg-8 mx-auto lead">Our dedicated team of developers and designers is committed to creating an app that not only meets your needs but exceeds your expectations. We are passionate about mental health and strive to make a meaningful impact on the lives of our users.</p>

        <p class="col-lg-8 mx-auto lead">Thank you for choosing MoodMinder to be a part of your mental wellness journey. If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out to us. We're here to support you!</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">How are you feeling? <span class="text-body-secondary">Slide to select.</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Joyful or Sad? Angry or Scared? MoodMinder has a simple slider feature to allow you to choose what level of emotion you are feeling for each of the seven universal emotions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="500" src="/img/snapshot.png" alt="Snapshot Image" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">What have you been up to? <span class="text-body-secondary">Select activity tags</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Add the activities that you have been doing during the day that have triggered that specific emotional response. You can also add notes, like an old school diary.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
          <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="500" src="/img/triggers.PNG" alt="Triggers Image" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>





  <%- include('_footer') %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>